<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row g-3 ">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h1 class="mb-3">
                Secure Interviews. Now free for everyone.
            </h1>
            <p style="color: #5F6368;">We re-engineered the service we built for secure business meetings, Connect Us,
                to make it free and
                available for all.</p>
            <div class="a123 my-5" style="display: flex; ">
                <a class="btn btn-primary new-meeting" style="width: 180px;" href="/new-meeting" role="button">New
